        {
            "+content": "In the distant future, the war between the human race and the Gamilon has taken its toll on the planet Earth. Constant bombardment by radioactive asteroids has rendered the planet's atmosphere uninhabitable. As a means of relief aid, Queen Starsha of the planet Iscandar offers the Earth Forces a device that can completely neutralize the radiation off the planet. For this task, the space battleship <i>Yamato</i> is launched from the remains of its World War II ancestor on a 148,000 light-year journey. However, the crew of the <i>Yamato</i> has only one Earth year to travel to Iscandar and back, or the human race will come to an end. <em class=de-emphasized>(from TV)</em>",
